model.name: Masison2022 - Liver Iron Metabolism with updated ferritin

body.p: This is a new version of a liver iron model (original from Mitchell 2013 BIOMD0000000498) with updated kinetics of ferritin iron storage. It uses MODEL2211030001 as a substitute for the original ferritin reactions.
